<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link href="~/HP_Assets/assets/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/HP_Assets/assets/css/base.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/HP_Assets/assets/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-z3gLpd7yknf1YoNbCzqRKc4qyor8gaKU1qmn+CShxbuBusANI9QpRohGBreCFkKxLhei6S9CQXFEbbKuqLg0DA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <!-- <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous"> -->
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="col-12" style="height: 55px;">
            <div class="header">
                <div class="header-nav__one">
                    <div class="nav-VNEN">
                        <span>
                            <img src="https://nhaxinh.com/wp-content/plugins/sitepress-multilingual-cms/res/flags/vi.png" alt="Tiếng Việt">
                            <span style="color: grey;">VN</span> EN
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nav">
                        <ul class="nav-list">
                            <li class="nav-list__item">
                                <a href="#" class="item-link item-link__call">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-phone item-link__call--icon"></i>
                                    1800 7200
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-list__item">
                                <a href="#" class="item-link">

                                    Giới thiệu
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-list__item">
                                <a href="#" class="item-link">

                                    Khuyến mãi
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-list__item">
                                <span href="#" class="item-link item-link__sale">

                                    Giảm giá đặc biệt
                                </span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="header__navbar-list">
                    <li class="header__navbar-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-location-arrow header__navbar-item-icon"></i>
                    </li>
                    <li class="header__navbar-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-heart header__navbar-item-icon"></i>
                    </li>
                    <li class="header__navbar-item">
                        <a href="~/HP_GioHang/Index"><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping header__navbar-item-icon"></i></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="header__navbar-item">
                        <a href="~/HP_DangNhap/Index" class="header__navbar-item-link">Đăng nhập</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="header__navbar-item">
                        <a href="~/HP_DangKy/Index" class="header__navbar-item-link">Đăng ký</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-2" style="height: 70px;">
            <div class="bag">
                <!-- Navbar -->
                <label for="nav__input-checkbox" class="nav__bars-btn">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bars bag-category"></i>
                </label>

                <input type="checkbox" hidden name="" class="nav__input" id="nav__input-checkbox">

                <label for="nav__input-checkbox" class="nav__overlay"></label>

                <nav class="nav__bag">
                    <label for="nav__input-checkbox" class="nav__close">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
                    </label>
                    <ul class="nav__list">
                        <li class="nav__list-item">
                            <a href="#" class="nav__link">SOFA</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav__list-item">
                            <a href="#" class="nav__link">BÀN</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav__list-item">
                            <a href="#" class="nav__link">GHẾ</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav__list-item">
                            <a href="#" class="nav__link">GIƯỜNG NGỦ</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav__list-item">
                            <a href="#" class="nav__link">TỦ VÀ KỆ</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav__list-item">
                            <a href="#" class="nav__link">BẾP</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>

                <!-- LOGO -->
                <a href="~/HP_TrangChu/Index" class="logo">
                    <img src="~/HP_Assets/assets/img/logo.jpg" alt="Nội thất HP" class="logo__img">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dropdown -->
        <div class="col-7" style="height: 70px;">
            <div class="header-navbar">
                <ul class="navbar-list">
                    <li class="navbar-list__item">
                        <a href="" class="navbar-list__link">
                            <div class="dropdown">
                                <div class="dropdown__select">
                                    <span class="dropdown__selected">Sản phẩm</span>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-down"></i>
                                </div>
                                <ul class="dropdown__list">
                                    @if (ViewBag.dropActive == 1)
                                    {
                                        <li class="dropdown__item">
                                            <a href="~/HP_SP_Sofa/Index" class="dropdown__text dropdown__active">
                                                Sofa
                                            </a>
                                        </li>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <li class="dropdown__item">
                                            <a href="~/HP_SP_Sofa/Index" class="dropdown__text">
                                                Sofa
                                            </a>
                                        </li>
                                    }
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Bàn
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Ghế
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Giường ngủ
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Tủ và kệ
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Bếp
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="navbar-list__item">
                        <a href="" class="navbar-list__link">
                            <div class="dropdown">
                                <div class="dropdown__select">
                                    <span class="dropdown__selected">Phòng</span>
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-down"></i>
                                </div>
                                <ul class="dropdown__list">
                                    @if (ViewBag.dropActive == 7)
                                    {
                                        <li class="dropdown__item">
                                            <a href="~/HP_P_PhongKhach" class="dropdown__text dropdown__active">
                                                Phòng khách
                                            </a>
                                        </li>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <li class="dropdown__item">
                                            <a href="~/HP_P_PhongKhach" class="dropdown__text">
                                                Phòng khách
                                            </a>
                                        </li>
                                    }
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Phòng ăn
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Phòng ngủ
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="dropdown__item">
                                        <a href="#" class="dropdown__text">
                                            Phòng làm việc
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    @if (ViewBag.Active == 3)
                    {
                        <li class="navbar-list__item active__navbar">
                            <a href="~/HP_BoSuuTap/Index" class="navbar-list__link">
                                Bộ sưu tập
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <li class="navbar-list__item">
                            <a href="~/HP_BoSuuTap/Index" class="navbar-list__link">
                                Bộ sưu tập
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    }
                    @if (ViewBag.Active == 4)
                    {
                        <li class="navbar-list__item active__navbar">
                            <a href="~/HP_ThietKeNoiThat/Index" class="navbar-list__link">
                                Thiết kế nội thất
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <li class="navbar-list__item">
                            <a href="~/HP_ThietKeNoiThat/Index" class="navbar-list__link">
                                Thiết kế nội thất
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    }
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-3" style="height: 70px;">
            <div class="header-search">
                <input type="text" class="header-search__input" placeholder="Tìm kiếm">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass header-search__icon"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="col-12" style="height: 117px;"></div>
    <!-- End Header -->

    @RenderBody()

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer__bag">
            <div class="col-3 footer__bg" style="height: 200px;">
                <h4 class="footer__title">KẾT NỐI VỚI HP FURNITURE</h4>
                <ul class="footer__list">
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        HP FURNITURE
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        FOLLOW US
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        <a href="">Instagram - Youtube - Facebook</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-3 footer__bg" style="height: 200px;">
                <h4 class="footer__title">HP FURNITURE</h4>
                <ul class="footer__list">
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Giới thiệu
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Tổng công ty
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Tuyển dụng
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Thẻ hội viên
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Đổi trả hàng
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-3 footer__bg" style="height: 200px;">
                <h4 class="footer__title">CẢM HỨNG #HP FURNITURE</h4>
                <ul class="footer__list">
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Sản phẩm
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Ý tưởng và cảm hứng
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-3 footer__bg" style="height: 200px;">
                <h4 class="footer__title">NEWSLETTER</h4>
                <ul class="footer__list">
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Hãy để lại email của bạn để nhận được những ý tưởng trang trí mới và những thông tin, ưu đãi từ Nhà Xinh
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Email: tunhienbikick.com.vn
                    </li>
                    <li class="footer__list-item">
                        Hotline: 18007200
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-1 footer__bg" style="height: 150px;"></div>
        <div class="col-10 footer__bg" style="height: 150px;">
            <div class="footer__balo">
                <div>
                    © 2021 - Bản quyền của tunhienbikick - thương hiệu thuộc HP Furniture <br>
                    Từ năm 1999 - thương hiệu đăng ký số 284074 Cục sở hữu trí tuệ
                </div>
                <div><img src="https://nhaxinh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/image-15.png" alt=""></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-1 footer__bg" style="height: 150px;"></div>
    </footer>


    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.js"></script>
    <script src="~/HP_Assets/validator.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

